oracle.adf.view.rich.remote

Class TaskInvocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.adf.view.rich.remote.TaskInvocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TaskInvocation
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Stores information about a task invocation for this request. These objects are created in the RemoteApplicationRequest addTask method. Largely this class is used by the remote adf applications implementation to execute the various task handlers and record thier results.
    Since:
    12.1.4.0
